{"tid":2494812,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"憑呢一首歌我敢講「張敬軒」係香港樂壇歷史第一人","createTime":"2021-04-18T20:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T21:52:28.000Z","uid":366207,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ae8309ae2446b576ba40bc1008827fab9dec6f","tid":2494812,"uid":366207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T20:48:22.000Z","msg":"成首歌 無論係 詞 曲 節奏 音準 氣氛 張敬軒既演繹都係頂尖<br />\n<br />\n由前面慢節奏 營造一個痴心 痛不欲生既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到2:01 眼神變化 壓低把聲 第一句 「立什麼心腸 我對你極善良 如若你肯想想我這樣受傷」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻轉化為一個 「<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">恨</span></span>」字<br />\n撕心裂肺既感覺 <br />\n<br />\n再到3:25-3:35 呢10秒既吶喊推到上高潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再到最後一段 終於醒悟既感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成首歌只可以用兩個字概括<br />\n「<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">完美！</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wOUovyr0icE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwOUovyr0icE&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpq7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=d74d5b1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wOUovyr0icE</a>"},{"pid":"e3c8ef37ceed658271aa3dd428849d80fbf64912","tid":2494812,"uid":343574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T20:49:34.000Z","msg":"抵呀，抵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11de624f0cc33378db4618be2acc72ff105e4db4","tid":2494812,"uid":366207,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T20:54:04.000Z","msg":"真心講句 琴晚viutv成班人合埋<br />\n都唔會夠張敬軒黎"},{"pid":"d13fcc7bf7ab01092909d5ae3bf722e3f900d318","tid":2494812,"uid":393544,"like":1,"dislike":5,"s